@1004 = ~Shield Amulet~
@1005 = ~Made by the Harpell clan of wizards in Longsaddle, these simple but elegant amulets generate a large shield-sized invisible wall of force that stays with the wearer and protects him as if it were a normal shield. This special creation can be activated and deactivated at will, and so does not encumber nor does it interfere with arcane spellcasting.

