@1014 = ~Kaligun's Amulet of Magic Resistance~
@1015 = ~This particular amulet has the initials KP on its back surface. KP, or Kaligun Poonil, was the general of a small force sent into the woodlands to clear out Red Wizards. Being particularly fearful of magic, he wore this amulet along with other magical protections. Overconfident in these protections, Kaligun finally died when he foolishly ambushed three high level Red Wizards who lowered his magic resistance before destroying him with their spells.

