@1018 = ~Periapt of Proof Against Poison~
@1019 = ~This periapt, which has to be be worn next to the skin, makes the wearer immune to all poisons. Items with similar functions are in common circulation, created for nobles or merchants fearing poison. Eunuchs from Kara-Tur wear amulets such as this when sampling their emperor's food, and The Purple Dragons use rings with similar powers to protect the Obarskyr royal family from assassination attempts.

