@1101 = ~Belt of Inertial Barrier~
@1102 = ~When worn, this belt creates a dense curtain of air around the wearer, forming a barrier which provides superior protection against breath attacks as well as missile weapons. The barrier is not strong enough to keep enemies out, but it can slow them a bit. By the scorch marks on the worn leather, it is obvious that this belt has been worn at least once against a dragon.

