@1687 = ~Dark Elven Spellchain +3~
@1688 = ~This mail feels more akin to cloth than to metal, and may be worn by thieves with few penalties and by fighter-mages without impairing their spellcasting ability. This variety of mail is woven in almost exactly the same form by both elves and drows; its design has changed little since the drow's elven past and is used for surface forays, where drowcrafted chain would decay.

