@1707 = ~This is a small animal figurine.~
@1708 = ~This small figurine is a perfect replication of a lion. When the command word is spoken, the lion grows to normal proportions, becoming a living, breathing cat named Joolon. The lion obeys the summoner's commands. The lion remains for five minutes, or until slain, at which point it once again becomes a figurine. Joolon, being magically created, is immune to normal weapons. After five minutes, regardless of whether the lion lived or died, the figurine returns and it takes a day to recharge it.

